title: Holiday Jazz Music Collection 2017
description:
Holiday Jazz Music Collection 2017

Here's a large collection of Christmas / Holiday music albums of jazz, and some other types like Rock and Pop music as well.  Hopefully it will put you in the mood for the short and cold days this time of year.  Cheers to everyone and please try to get along with your family and neighbors!
